I couldn't sleep. Can you read to me?

20:22.881 --> 20:24.781
O-Of course. Let me...

20:24.806 --> 20:25.874
Uh-oh.

20:25.899 --> 20:28.710
Grover, whoa, whoa, whoa, little man.

20:29.114 --> 20:32.098
In this house, we all
stay in our own beds.

